(6, 4, 'TOGETHER WITH PLAYPLAY', 'üé• 1-Click AI videos: Boost efficiency, amplify your reach', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/d72d4727-16b1-47fb-9300-97ef2f9d20ab/PlayPlay_Visual__1_.png?t=1708902225', NULL, '<b>The Rundown:</b> <br> With PlayPlay, anyone can create studio-quality videos in minutes using its AI ‚Äì no editing skills required.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>PlayPlay lets you:</b>\r\n<br>\r\nStart a new video using a simple text prompt.\r\n<br>\r\nInstantly add captions with one click.\r\n<br>\r\nTranslate videos into 120+ languages and bring your story to life with AI voice-overs.\r\n<br>\r\nClick here to try PlayPlay‚Äôs AI video creation platform, already trusted by leading brands like Dell, SAS, and L‚ÄôOreal.', '2024-02-26 11:07:03', '2024-02-26 04:07:03'),
(7, 4, 'FIGURE AI', 'ü§ñ Tech titans back Figure AI in $675 funding round', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/f90ffc31-5a94-45e5-9367-35abc51ffbed/figure-ai.jpg?t=1708904356', 'Figure', '<p><strong>The Rundown: </strong>Humanoid robotics startup Figure AI has reportedly <a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5ibG9vbWJlcmcuY29tL25ld3MvYXJ0aWNsZXMvMjAyNC0wMi0yMy9iZXpvcy1udmlkaWEtam9pbi1vcGVuYWktbWljcm9zb2Z0LWluLWZ1bmRpbmctaHVtYW5vaWQtcm9ib3Qtc3RhcnR1cC1maWd1cmUtYWk_.YTJyBEEq8sC2zoLuvkLwG4toc_D4-plVsAfmDjNSUEQ\"><strong>secured</strong></a> a massive $675M funding round led by tech giants including Jeff Bezos, Nvidia, Microsoft, and OpenAI.</p><p><strong>The details:</strong></p><ul><li>Bezos committed $100M, alongside Microsoft ($95M), Nvidia ($50M), Intel ($25M), Samsung ($5M) and more.</li><li>OpenAI and Microsoft initially led the round, and had even reportedly previously considered acquiring the robotics startup.</li><li>Figure aims to create robots that safely take on labor shortages in repetitive or hazardous jobs, with a recent <a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.._VFb4lqBgacagwWHW_8MYglnOJC0Svc0mjg9P7__-4Y\"><strong>partnership</strong></a> placing the tech in BMW‚Äôs car manufacturing plant.</li><li>Figure AI\'s pre-money valuation reaches roughly $2B with the new investments.</li></ul><p><strong>Why it matters: </strong>It‚Äôs not every day you see Amazon, Microsoft, Nvidia, OpenAI, and other tech titans all on the same project, but the race to get humanoid robots to market is heating up ‚Äî and everyone wants in. Expect the tech to get here a LOT sooner than people think.</p>', NULL, '2024-02-27 08:26:55'),
(8, 4, 'AI TRAINING', 'üìù Automate meeting notes with Notion AI', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/7384fe03-fd47-4681-a3ef-91676e783931/Screenshot_2024-02-25_at_6.53.37_PM.png?t=1708916023', 'AI', '<p><strong>The Rundown:</strong> Using Notion AI, you can automatically summarize meetings, generate topic tags, capture tasks, organize meeting notes, and more with ‚Äòauto-fill properties‚Äô.</p><ol><li>Go to <a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..uJ5TcItpkFv1W36Y0szev8V40YzAW6qIdpc5JvUov14\"><strong>Notion</strong></a> or open the Notion app.</li><li>Establish a database for meeting notes, incorporating relevant properties. For example, the meeting date, attendees, a summary, topics discussed, and tasks assigned.</li><li>Enable Notion AI to autofill fields that can be generated from your meeting notes.</li><li>To do this, select \'Property\', then \'Edit Property\', then \'AI Auto-fill\', and finally, insert the prompt or list of tags.</li></ol><p><strong>Bonus tip:</strong> Enable the \'Auto Update on Page Edits\' feature so your properties stay up-to-date!</p>', NULL, '2024-03-08 04:43:52'),
(11, 6, 'ANTHROPIC', 'üèÜ Anthropic releases Claude 3 and new benchmarks', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/1c69325c-fd37-4167-b559-95e19561fb8c/claud3.jpg?t=1709579812', 'Anthropic', '<b>The Rundown:</b> Anthropic just announced the release of its next-generation Claude 3 model family, with the top-tier ‚ÄòOpus‚Äô version outperforming top models like GPT-4 and Gemini Ultra across major benchmarks.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>The details:</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\nThe Claude 3 lineup consists of Opus, Sonnet, and Haiku, each offering different levels of capability, speed, and cost.\r\n<br> <br>\r\nOpus outperforms GPT-4 and Gemini Ultra on benchmarks, including expert knowledge, reasoning, coding, and mathematics.\r\n<br><br>\r\nClaude 3 also claims new vision capabilities on par with leading models like GPT-4V.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOpus displays a near-perfect 99% recall ability on processing long context prompts.\r\n<br><br>\r\nAll three models boast a 200k context window (with the ability to handle as high as 1M).\r\n<br><br>\r\nClaude has removed the waitlist for API usage, allowing builders to immediately integrate the enhanced new models.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Why it matters:</b><br> Gemini and ChatGPT may have gotten all the headlines in 2024, but Claude just came out of nowhere to claim the top of the AI benchmark leaderboards. We‚Äôll be sharing the results from The Rundown‚Äôs Claude 3 vs. GPT-4 tests shortly ‚Äî stay tuned!\r\n<br><br>\r\nYou can try Claude 3 or access the API here.', '2024-03-05 20:41:02', '2024-03-05 13:47:56'),
(19, 28, 'MILITARY AI', 'U.S Army explores GPT-4 as a battle adviser', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/23445672-67d5-41ca-8a72-a894286b9339/military.jpg?t=1709673885', 'DALL-E 3', '<p><strong>The Rundown: </strong>The US Army Research Lab is reportedly <a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..GnvuLl8xNf8VQD7tjwNuQ7utyFWUT-UPOLPbb0WwYoU\"><strong>testing</strong></a> commercial AI chatbots like GPT-4 as battlefield planning assistants in war game simulations.</p><p><strong>The details:</strong></p><ul><li>In an experiment, AI chatbots proposed battle plans for a war scenario in the game StarCraft II.</li><li>OpenAI\'s GPT-4 outperformed other AI models tested, though they were still imperfect.</li><li>The DoD has identified a whopping 180 possible military uses for AI, working with copmpanies like Palantir and Scale AI to integrate the tech.</li><li>Experts caution against using AI for military decisions, citing feasibility and ethical/bias concerns.</li></ul><p><strong>Why it matters: </strong>While AI‚Äôs integration in warfare is unavoidable, its use on the battlefield still raises troubling ethical and moral questions. But as the AI arms race heats up between global powers, the pressure to deploy the tech to gain a military advantage will only grow ‚Äî whether or not it is truly ready for use.</p>', NULL, '2024-03-07 08:08:32'),
(20, 28, 'TOGETHER WITH AE STUDIO', 'üß† Stay ahead of the AI curve with AE Studio', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/baa05a47-bd4d-4e5b-b2a1-2ca3727157c0/AE_Ad_Visual_25__3_.png?t=1709667689', NULL, '<p><strong>The Rundown:</strong> Accelerate your company\'s success with AE Studio\'s proven approach to building high-impact custom software and AI solutions.</p><ul><li>Turbocharge your product development and save hundreds of hours</li><li>Have industry experts build your custom software and AI solutions</li><li>Hire AE to pinpoint what you should be building and where to find ROI</li></ul><p><a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..a-uRCP_aX783xaFIzEyuSDdfrKDF_brXE_QRbJ8UC8Y\"><strong>Book your FREE strategy session with AE Studio today</strong></a> to learn more and see why AE is the go-to partner for startups and enterprise.</p>', NULL, '2024-03-07 08:08:32'),
(21, 28, 'STABILITY AI', 'üßä Stability AI drops rapid 3D object generator', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/96f0f601-17c4-42c1-b60a-26c931e7434e/3dstability.jpg?t=1709667578', 'Stability AI', '<p><strong>The Rundown: </strong>Stability AI just partnered with Tripo AI to <a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..jnqxNXcpvJwrNjg63iVQOcS7WgIRBgekHrq8NKWywtg\"><strong>release</strong></a> TripoSR, a new state-of-the-art model that generates near-instant, high-quality 3D objects from a single image.</p><p><strong>The details:</strong></p><ul><li>TripoSR uses an AI system with millions of parameters to analyze a 2D image and predict a 3D representation of the object.</li><li>The model was trained on a massive dataset of nearly 1M 3D objects, including both synthetic renderings and real-world captures.</li><li>TripoSR runs efficiently without requiring a high-end GPU, making it widely accessible for use in design, gaming, AR/VR, and beyond.</li></ul><p><strong>Why it matters: </strong>With its impressive speed and quality, TripoSR represents a major leap forward in AI-powered 3D creation. By enabling nearly instant generations from a single photo, the tech could revolutionize workflows and empower more creators to bring their visions to life in 3D.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>', NULL, '2024-03-07 08:08:32'),
(22, 28, 'AI TRAINING', 'ü•ä Comparing Claude 3 vs. ChatGPT', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/a79962e9-878f-4e68-ac8c-5992150be1a4/Copy_of_Copy_of_Copy_of_PRO.png?t=1709678682', NULL, '<p><strong>The Rundown:</strong> Anthropic just released Claude 3, setting new industry benchmarks across a wide range of tasks.</p><p><strong>Here are a couple of tests we ran for </strong><a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovL2NsYXVkZS5haS8_.2ztTwj64G7POI87DBCrzptBXYofW1Ve3nuvKDPfH-gE\"><strong>Claude 3</strong></a><strong> (Opus) vs. </strong><a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovL2NoYXQub3BlbmFpLmNvbS8_.2dfF6deKObzAg_mfA80D5GG0ho_-arR4uZMAKrw0CRw\"><strong>ChatGPT</strong></a><strong> (GPT-4):</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Content writing: </strong>When asked the question, ‚ÄúWrite a blog post about the benefits of traveling to other countries,‚Äù Claude responded more naturally and less robotically than ChatGPT.</li><li><strong>Coding an app: </strong>When the task was to code a colorful currency converter app, Claude did a better job in following the instructions and making it colorful. ChatGPT‚Äôs app was functional but very plain.</li><li><strong>Math:</strong> It‚Äôs well-known that LLMs are not good with prime numbers. Surprisingly, ChatGPT answered correctly when asked ‚ÄúIs 29593 a prime number?‚Äù, while Claude did not.</li><li><strong>Creative writing:</strong> ‚ÄúWrite ten sentences that end with ‚Äòth‚Äô‚Äù. ChatGPT did 4 out of 10 correctly, while Claude got right 5 out of 10.</li></ul>', NULL, '2024-03-07 08:08:32'),
(23, 28, 'PRESENTED BY COVALENT', 'üêç Serverless H100s with one line of code', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/07c14500-ac45-450a-aec1-113f871531ee/image1__10_.png?t=1709667772', NULL, '<p><strong>The Rundown:</strong> Covalent provides instant access to serverless GPUs like H100s, A100s, L40s, and RTXs, entirely in Python. No reservations needed ‚Äì only pay for what you use.</p><p><strong>With Covalent, you get:</strong></p><ul><li>AI infrastructure with a single Python decorator</li><li>Only pay for the resources you consume</li><li>No reservations or minimum spend required</li></ul><p><a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..7EFCQDmqv9mwwC01NMEbs69GgvxhpkAbb4d3LGKZWsE\"><strong>Sign up today</strong></a><strong> and get $20 in free credits.</strong></p>', NULL, '2024-03-07 08:09:45'),
(24, 29, 'OPENAI', 'üò± OpenAI‚Äôs recent discovery before firing Sam Altman', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/5022a704-bef9-46c0-b325-aeea7c5bb243/Screenshot_2023-11-23_at_10.25.22_PM.png?t=1700807146', 'Jessica Chou via WIRED', '<p><strong>The Rundown: </strong>According to a report by <a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..Ar2AKGraZfU62XdjDuS0Jz9zPqe149gEbSslOlMnVXs\"><strong>Reuters</strong></a>, OpenAI had a secret breakthrough called Q* (pronounced Q-Star) that precipitated the firing of Sam Altman.</p><p><strong>The details:</strong></p><ul><li>Before Sam\'s firing, researchers sent the board a letter warning of a new AI discovery that could \"threaten humanity.\"</li><li>The new model dubbed Q* demonstrated internal capabilities of doing simple math (something <i>no model</i> has achieved).</li><li>While simple math might not seem impressive to most, it could be a huge step toward creating artificial general intelligence (AGI).</li><li>A day before Sam was fired, he gave a chilling speech, <a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..RAfyGy3NRYVJLrnhsup64z8BUmEH7BH80ESmyfunkbM\"><strong>quoting</strong></a>: \"Is this a tool we\'ve built or a creature we have built?\"</li></ul><p><strong>Why it matters: </strong>While Q* is not fully confirmed yet, if true, the entire firing of Sam Altman could have been AGI-related all along, and the board‚Äôs drastic (and unexplained) actions would make more sense.</p>', NULL, '2024-03-08 04:48:02'),
(25, 29, 'TOGETHER WITH MINDVALLEY', 'üß† Turn your online presence into a digital powerhouse', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/3b11d59e-520e-46e7-b62a-82f09de8fc9d/1920_x_1080_6_speakers__1_.jpeg?t=1700788304', NULL, '<p><strong>The Rundown: </strong>Join leading social media experts at Mindvalley\'s free online Summit. Learn from influencers and strategists who\'ve captivated millions.</p><p><strong>Explore key topics:</strong></p><ul><li>Crafting Viral Brands</li><li>Converting Followers</li><li>Creative Content with AI</li><li>Mastering Organic Social Media Reach</li></ul><p>Whether you\'re a CEO amplifying your brand, an entrepreneur monetizing your following, or an advocate promoting a cause, this summit offers the insights and tools you need.</p><p><a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..vy7QK7LSCW-2NY32QwOxpiI3gXge2oMxtOEm-N3PFAI\"><strong>Click to Unlock Your Free Pass for the 3-Day Summit</strong></a></p>', NULL, '2024-03-08 04:48:02'),
(26, 29, 'xAI', 'üëΩ xAI plans to launch Grok next week to rival ChatGPT', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/d6e852ef-30d9-4a5b-9646-1c8d2dcb2568/Screenshot_2023-11-23_at_8.58.16_PM.png?t=1700801931', 'xAI', '<p><strong>The Rundown: </strong>Elon Musk‚Äôs new company, xAI, is <a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..YGqO-T27XS_YUfUXypRvAj1vxFIHFEb0sy-V4ldhYEE\"><strong>reportedly</strong></a> launching Grok, its ChatGPT competitor next week to X Premium+ subscribers.</p><p><strong>The details:</strong></p><ul><li>Grok will be integrated directly into X (formerly Twitter) and will have its own unique tab within the platform.</li><li>Grok‚Äôs differentiation over ChatGPT is its unique features like a <i>distinctive</i> personality and real-time X knowledge access.</li><li>Grok is part of a new, higher-priced X Premium+ subscription, priced at $16/month (above the standard $8/month).</li><li>Users will be able to submit feedback on how Grok answered, including writing optimal answers in response, to train the AI over time.</li></ul><p><strong>Our thoughts: </strong>While X is known to be the top platform for real-time news, it‚Äôs also known for massive misinformation. Given this fact, it will be interesting to see how the team at xAI handles what to feed into the AI vs. not.</p>', NULL, '2024-03-08 04:49:17'),
(32, 32, 'OPENAI', 'üò± Elon Musk sues Sam Altman and OpenAI', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/5f45b1a0-9047-4594-a0bf-20abc3f0f31f/muskaltman.jpg?t=1709504056', 'Getty Images / Reuters', '<p><strong>The Rundown: </strong>Elon Musk just <a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..Flf8R8fj9HIhWJL9Xy4rNK9XbJN9KVLa_gWPoLvbEWU\"><strong>sued</strong></a> OpenAI and CEO Sam Altman over claims that the AI firm abandoned its founding mission to benefit humanity in favor of profits with Microsoft.</p><p><strong>The details:</strong></p><ul><li>The lawsuit claims OpenAI breached its nonprofit charter and licensing terms by keeping GPT-4 secret and proprietary.</li><li>Musk seeks to force OpenAI back to its original mission of developing open and safe AGI technology, which he believes has shifted since helping co-found the company in 2015.</li><li>Musk also believes the new board lacks the expertise to determine if breakthroughs like the rumored Q* system reach AGI.</li><li>The filing also highlights the <a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..Xt-Ck5I1gxKggmLIoMsj7S7EwF_gYM1XZMAvR6aefxY\"><strong>complexity</strong></a> of OpenAI‚Äôs corporate structure, with 8 different sub-companies listed in the lawsuit.</li></ul><p><strong>Why it matters: </strong>Elon Musk\'s history with OpenAI adds a new layer of intrigue to the most captivating story in tech. While the lawsuit\'s outcome is uncertain, it is likely to uncover several mysteries surrounding OpenAI, including the departure of Ilya Sutskever, the Q* breakthrough, and more. Stay tuned‚Ä¶</p>', NULL, '2024-03-14 02:59:55'),
(33, 32, 'TOGETHER WITH HUBSPOT', 'üî• Empower your workflow with ChatGPT', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/76884563-ca11-4839-b27b-99ace11e9e4e/image1__9_.png?t=1709396988', NULL, '<p><strong>The Rundown:</strong> With Hubspot‚Äôs free ChatGPT guide, you can learn real-world tips to boost productivity, automate tasks, and maximize AI‚Äôs potential in your work.</p><p><strong>You‚Äôll learn how to:</strong></p><ul><li>Enhance work efficiency and boost productivity with ChatGPT.</li><li>Apply ChatGPT to everyday work challenges with real-world applications.</li><li>Gain insights about generative AI‚Äôs impact on business and the future of work.</li></ul><p><a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovL29mZmVycy5odWJzcG90LmNvbS91c2luZy1jaGF0Z3B0LWF0LXdvcms_.L5to1gCkVyd7GU7W7NJT4jyr6ebHLVUYK1u4Y7WWhXs\"><strong>Download the guide for free.</strong></a></p>', NULL, '2024-03-14 02:59:55'),
(34, 32, 'CHATGPT', 'üó£Ô∏è ChatGPT quietly rolls out ‚ÄòRead Aloud‚Äô', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/e081995c-b5b7-498d-b520-999afe78b649/speechchat.png?t=1709522961', '@teddynae on X', '<p><strong>The Rundown: </strong>A new ChatGPT feature called ‚ÄòRead Aloud‚Äò has been quietly rolling out to a select group of users on both mobile and desktop versions, with no official announcement from OpenAI.</p><p><strong>The details:</strong></p><ul><li>Read Aloud allows ChatGPT to read the answers it generates aloud using an AI-generated voice.</li><li>Users can select and change the voice of ChatGPT in settings, with five options currently available: Ember, Breeze, Cove, Juniper, and Sky.</li><li>The rollout of Read Aloud appears to be limited to a small number of users, but we expect an official announcement and broader rollout shortly.</li><li>Images were obtained via direct message to our team from the user <a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..LbwH4yxjtGpYy_yGqNDBm3CMfgEJRoBMJqzSzy3uc9A\"><strong>@TeddyNAE</strong></a> on X.</li></ul><p><strong>Why it matters: </strong>While ChatGPT\'s voice memo feature on its mobile app is a great conversational partner, it was lacking one important quality: the ability to respond via voice. The new feature will now allow ChatGPT to read messages it generates back to users ‚Äî greatly increase accessibility to the tech.</p>', NULL, '2024-03-14 02:59:55'),
(35, 32, 'AI TRAINING', 'üé® Transform any picture into a sticker', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/16eb2aa0-0020-4bba-bd78-1ae98fa6918b/arnold.png?t=1709511142', NULL, '<p><strong>The Rundown:</strong> In this tutorial, you will learn how to turn any image into a sticker, unlocking endless possibilities for customizing your digital and physical spaces.</p><p><strong>Step-by-step:</strong></p><ol><li>Visit the ‚Äúface-to-sticker‚Äù model in <a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovL3JlcGxpY2F0ZS5jb20vZm9mci9mYWNlLXRvLXN0aWNrZXI_.ejBNhhk-o6VkL8nihTVs0u0n1t23MxbvjH4K9O9f_kI\"><strong>Replicate</strong></a>. You can try it completely free.</li><li>Select a good picture and upload it. Ideally, choose an image where there is enough contrast between a solid background and the main subject.</li><li>Edit the prompt to closely match your chosen picture and play around with the different settings the model offers, e.g., width, height, seeds, or even upscale.</li><li>Click ‚ÄúRun‚Äù and watch your image magically turn into a sticker üéâ</li></ol>', NULL, '2024-03-14 02:59:55'),
(36, 32, 'AI RESEARCH', 'üîã Microsoft‚Äôs 70x more energy-efficient LLM', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/22bf146a-e988-4431-989d-1bf4bb8c4dc5/GHobBjRb0AAngOl.jpeg?t=1709516199', 'Microsoft Research', '<p><strong>The Rundown: </strong>Microsoft Research just published a new <a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovL2FyeGl2Lm9yZy9wZGYvMjQwMi4xNzc2NC5wZGY_.zWEQx9Q1TBAYCnLPrwPNBU9-1SoiWCszkvu3KtZDhho\"><strong>paper</strong></a> titled <i>‚ÄúThe Era of 1-bit LLMs‚Äù</i>, introducing a new LLM variant breakthrough that‚Äôs just 1-bit in size, called BitNet b1.58.</p><p><strong>The details:</strong></p><ul><li>BitNet b1.58 is a 1.58-bit LLM variant where every parameter is ternary {-1, 0, 1}.</li><li>The LLM variant matches the performance of full-precision (FP16) LLMs starting from a 3B size.</li><li>It‚Äôs a whopping 70x more energy efficient and 4x smaller than LLaMA LLM.</li></ul><p><strong>Why it matters: </strong>With energy consumption being a critical challenge in scaling LLMs, BitNet b1.58 demonstrates a new approach to enable wider deployment of AI systems while maintaining performance and dramatically improving energy efficiency.</p>', NULL, '2024-03-14 02:59:55'),
(37, 33, 'GOOGLE DEEPMIND', 'üéÆ Google‚Äôs ‚ÄòGenie‚Äô enables prompt-to-games', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/37f4fdfa-aaf7-4740-a6ae-02e5bb53b8c7/genie.jpg?t=1708980303', 'Google', '<p><strong>The Rundown: </strong>Researchers at Google DeepMind just <a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovL2FyeGl2Lm9yZy9wZGYvMjQwMi4xNTM5MS5wZGY_.KNo6vP-d2r6zLkOl9D5JJXHp5t2MvWKPJ8YfyWFOr5Y\"><strong>unveiled</strong></a> Genie, an AI system that can generate interactive video games from just a text or image prompt ‚Äî without any prior training on game mechanics.</p><p><strong>The details:</strong></p><ul><li>The model was trained on over 200,000 hours of 2D platform game videos, learning to understand gameplay autonomously.</li><li>Users can control game characters and objects on a frame-by-frame basis despite Genie not being trained with action labels.</li><li>The foundation model can also determine who the main character is and enable a user to control that character in the generated world.</li><li>Genie is a research-only model for now and can only create games at 1 FPS ‚Äî limiting its current viability despite future promise.</li></ul><p><strong>Why it matters: </strong>Anyone will be able to create their own entirely imagined virtual worlds soon, and that‚Äôs a wild sentence to say out loud. The model‚Äôs ability to learn and develop world models is also a massive step towards general AI agents.</p><p>See Genie‚Äôs wild game generations in action <a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovL3NpdGVzLmdvb2dsZS5jb20vdmlldy9nZW5pZS0yMDI0L2hvbWU_.7lmXzSNMzlk5KtlI0FuQ67KNZT_V6SfJK4lmK2suCNA\"><strong>here</strong></a>.</p>', NULL, '2024-03-14 03:02:18'),
(40, 35, 'APPLE', 'ü§© Apple unveils new MM1 AI models', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/7def3d9b-be3a-4c9b-a947-ca74edcf0e1b/apple1.jpg?t=1710710543', 'Apple', '<p><strong>The Rundown: </strong>Apple researchers just <a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovL2FyeGl2Lm9yZy9wZGYvMjQwMy4wOTYxMS5wZGY_.maHbzs3TPlwSWyYdhiaMI7fNXPYobB9g3gGaS_2poxI\"><strong>published</strong></a> a new paper unveiling MM1, a family of multimodal AI models that combine visual and language understanding to enable advanced capabilities.</p><p><strong>The details:</strong></p><ul><li>MM1 models were trained on a carefully curated mix of image captions, image-text data, and text-only data.</li><li>The largest 30B parameter model showed a strong ability to learn from only a handful of examples and reason over multiple images.</li><li>The research found that&nbsp;scaling the model‚Äôs image processing had the biggest impact on performance.</li><li>MM1‚Äôs benchmarks compete with state-of-the-art multimodal models like GPT-4V and Gemini Pro.</li></ul><p><strong>Why it matters: </strong>Apple‚Äôs level of detail and lack of fanfare for this model release is a big departure from its typical secrecy ‚Äî and a massive win for open source. With a capable model now officially a reality, is it finally time for Siri to level up?</p>', NULL, '2024-03-19 03:34:09'),
(41, 35, 'TOGETHER WITH DENTORO', 'üß† Bring your AI vision to life', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/ef532ff6-832a-49d2-b871-fa66f549a57f/image__11_.png?t=1710697213', NULL, '<p><strong>The Rundown:</strong> Dentoro, a software engineering company founded by ex-Googlers and Harvard grads, can help you build an MVP or develop custom AI solutions at unbeatable prices.</p><p><strong>With Dentoro, you can:</strong></p><ul><li>Fast-track your AI project with MVPs starting at just $36/hour.</li><li>Benefit from tailored AI solutions to address specific business challenges and objectives.</li><li>Easily scale AI initiatives from prototype to production.</li></ul><p>Take advantage of Dentoro\'s expertise to build your next AI prototype. <a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..4DYPWY1ZL-nFlhKsetYoTd-73VulHoKg-VX9J8nS3bg\"><strong>Get started now and enjoy 30% off your first month.</strong></a></p>', NULL, '2024-03-19 03:34:09'),
(42, 36, 'AI REGULATION', 'EU approves sweeping AI rules', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/4f573ae0-3830-4b62-8148-b201b1d71cf9/ghost_z12_a_cartoon_image_of_EU_leaders_passing_sweeping_regula_c44d7123-613a-43e1-ba2a-eaac40286704.png?t=1710453823', 'Midjourney', '<p><strong>The Rundown: </strong>The European Parliament just <a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..0nYxGghSFjTu9rNUTjuofSkOQETmeTIt9Mma4H9AEis\"><strong>passed</strong></a> the landmark Artificial Intelligence Act, establishing the world\'s most comprehensive set of regulations for AI tech.</p><p><strong>The details:</strong></p><ul><li>Newly banned AI apps include biometric and facial recognition on sensitive characteristics, social scoring, and AI that manipulates behavior or exploits vulnerabilities.</li><li>High-risk AI, such as in infrastructure, education, and employment, will face strict obligations like risk assessment, transparency, and human oversight.</li><li>The law has drawn criticism from both sides ‚Äî with companies worrying it stifles competitiveness and watchdogs arguing it doesn\'t go far enough.</li><li>The rules will take effect in stages, with some applying as early as six months after the law enters into enforcement.</li></ul><p><strong>Why it matters: </strong>The AI Act positions itself as the global standard for regulation, but will it disadvantage EU-based AI companies in the process? Despite the critiques, the act is a big first move ‚Äî potentially influencing other countries‚Äô AI approaches and altering the trajectory of the industry.</p>', NULL, '2024-03-19 09:21:10'),
(43, 37, 'AI REGULATION', 'EU approves sweeping AI rules', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/4f573ae0-3830-4b62-8148-b201b1d71cf9/ghost_z12_a_cartoon_image_of_EU_leaders_passing_sweeping_regula_c44d7123-613a-43e1-ba2a-eaac40286704.png?t=1710453823', 'Midjourney', '<p><strong>The Rundown: </strong>The European Parliament just <a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..0nYxGghSFjTu9rNUTjuofSkOQETmeTIt9Mma4H9AEis\"><strong>passed</strong></a> the landmark Artificial Intelligence Act, establishing the world\'s most comprehensive set of regulations for AI tech.</p><p><strong>The details:</strong></p><ul><li>Newly banned AI apps include biometric and facial recognition on sensitive characteristics, social scoring, and AI that manipulates behavior or exploits vulnerabilities.</li><li>High-risk AI, such as in infrastructure, education, and employment, will face strict obligations like risk assessment, transparency, and human oversight.</li><li>The law has drawn criticism from both sides ‚Äî with companies worrying it stifles competitiveness and watchdogs arguing it doesn\'t go far enough.</li><li>The rules will take effect in stages, with some applying as early as six months after the law enters into enforcement.</li></ul><p><strong>Why it matters: </strong>The AI Act positions itself as the global standard for regulation, but will it disadvantage EU-based AI companies in the process? Despite the critiques, the act is a big first move ‚Äî potentially influencing other countries‚Äô AI approaches and altering the trajectory of the industry.</p>', NULL, '2024-03-19 09:21:14'),
(44, 38, 'NEURALINK', 'üß† Neuralink patient plays chess with mind', 'https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/b2ac030a-2174-465e-addd-8fe38099b4dd/neuralink.jpg?t=1711049232', 'Neuralink', '<p><strong>The Rundown: </strong>Neuralink just <a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..lsnuqAY3497SlvHmVUGm3fdsgJEl0eMqFwAFtepatyw\"><strong>live-streamed</strong></a> their first patient using a brain-chip implant to play online chess and other games by mind control alone, in a major milestone for the technology.</p><p><strong>The details:</strong></p><ul><li>Noland Arbaugh, who is paralyzed from the shoulders down, demonstrated moving a cursor and playing chess using his the brain implant and his mind.</li><li>Arbaugh received the implant in January and reported no cognitive impairments, saying the surgery was \"super easy.\"</li><li>Using the implant, he played online chess and the video game Civilization VI for 8 hours straight.</li><li>Elon Musk also <a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovL3guY29tL2NiX2RvZ2Uvc3RhdHVzLzE3NzA1ODEwMDk1NzYxNjU3MjA_.XEp_wSCyz5SqwaaDxqU0KzrJk8LydSULj9S6jTzPUME\"><strong>revealed</strong></a> that Neuralink‚Äôs next product will be ‚ÄòBlindsight‚Äô, working to restore vision of people who were born blind.</li></ul><p><strong>Why it matters: </strong>Neuralink\'s patient demo is the latest evidence that brain-computer interfaces are rapidly progressing from science fiction to medical reality. While it‚Äôs easy to get caught up in dystopian narratives, this <a href=\"https://flight.beehiiv.net/v2/clicks/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..lsnuqAY3497SlvHmVUGm3fdsgJEl0eMqFwAFtepatyw\"><strong>video</strong></a> grounds us in the very real impact this technology could have.</p>', NULL, '2024-03-24 09:39:02'),
