(28, 'U.S. tests ChatGPT for military strategy', 'Stability AI\'s 3D object generator', '2024-03-07 15:08:32', '2024-03-07 08:17:31', 2, '<p>The U.S. Army is reportedly testing AI chatbots such as GPT-4 (ChatGPT) as battle advisors in military strategy simulations.</p><p>But is the tech ready? Let‚Äôs get into it‚Ä¶</p>'),
(29, 'OpenAI\'s secret discovery before firing Sam Altman', 'Grok is coming!', '2024-03-08 11:48:02', '2024-03-08 04:48:02', 2, '<p>The mystery of what led the OpenAI board to fire Sam Altman might‚Äôve just been solved.</p><p>A leak from top OpenAI researchers states they made a powerful AI discovery that could \"threaten humanity\" right before the ousting. Let‚Äôs get into it...</p>'),
(32, 'Elon Musk Vs. OpenAI', 'ChatGPT quietly rolls out new feature', '2024-03-14 09:59:55', '2024-03-14 02:59:55', 2, '<p>The latest lawsuit just got slammed on OpenAI‚Äôs doorway ‚Äî this time from none other than its former co-founder, Elon Musk.</p><p>But does Elon know something that we don‚Äôt, or is just jealousy of OpenAI‚Äôs recent success? Let‚Äôs get into it‚Ä¶</p>'),
(33, 'Google\'s new AI generates video games', 'Mistral\'s massive new model', '2024-03-14 10:02:18', '2024-03-14 03:02:18', 2, '<p>Google just rolled out a new AI model called ‚ÄòGenie‚Äò, and it could be a <i>game-changer</i>...</p><p>The AI can build video games from text or image prompts, opening the possibility for anyone to design their own playable worlds in the near future. Let‚Äôs get into it‚Ä¶</p>'),
(35, 'Apple\'s AI model revealed!', 'xAI officially open-sources Grok', '2024-03-19 10:34:09', '2024-03-19 03:34:09', 2, '<p>Apple\'s AI efforts have often been shrouded in secrecy, but the company just pulled back the curtain with the release of MM1.</p><p>The powerful new AI model could indicate a new era of AI for Apple ‚Äî and be the key to unlocking Siri\'s true potential. Let‚Äôs explore‚Ä¶</p>'),
(36, 'World\'s first major AI Act', 'Apple acquires an AI startup', '2024-03-19 16:21:10', '2024-03-19 09:21:10', 2, '<p>The AI revolution just got its first major set of ground rules, courtesy of the EU‚Äôs landmark AI Act.</p><p>But while the sweeping new legislation aims to reign in the tech‚Äôs most dangerous use cases, not everyone is convinced its the right approach. Let‚Äôs investigate‚Ä¶</p>'),
(37, 'World\'s first major AI Act', 'Apple acquires an AI startup', '2024-03-19 16:21:14', '2024-03-19 09:21:14', 2, '<p>The AI revolution just got its first major set of ground rules, courtesy of the EU‚Äôs landmark AI Act.</p><p>But while the sweeping new legislation aims to reign in the tech‚Äôs most dangerous use cases, not everyone is convinced its the right approach. Let‚Äôs investigate‚Ä¶</p>'),
